## Development

To set up the development environment:

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/pipenv-tools-hook.git
cd pipenv-tools-hook
```
2. Install development dependencies:
```bash
pip install hatch
```

3. Run tests:
```bash
hatch run test
```
4. Run type checking:
```bash
hatch run typecheck
```

5. Run linting:
```bash
hatch run lint
```

